data.title: Margaret Madaline Gardner Dickinson (1917
data.meta_description: Margaret Gardner Dickinson, 71, of Ogdensburg, NY, formerly of Taylor Settlement, Ellisburg, NY passed away Monday, March 6, 1989 at A. Barton Hepburn Hospital, Ogdensburg, where she had been a patient for two weeks.  Margaret, believed to have born in Lorraine, NY May 10, 1917, was a daughter  *(see NOTE below)  of...
